  "title": "Administrative Executive - Wealth Management",
  "description": "<p>📍 Raffles Place (Full-time)<br /><br />This is a hands-on support role working directly with a Wealth Manager, to support day-to-day client servicing and operational matters.<br /><br />In this role, you’ll be trusted to:</p><ul><li>Keep client documentation and submissions accurate, timely, and well-organised</li><li>Stay on top of ongoing cases so nothing slips through the cracks</li><li>Be the steady point of support that allows the Wealth Manager to focus on clients</li><li>Handle administrative work with professionalism, discretion, and consistency</li></ul><p><br />What you’ll gain</p><ul><li>Practical exposure to wealth management and advisory operations</li><li>Experience working closely with a seasoned Wealth Manager</li><li>A strong foundation in operations, client servicing, and financial administration</li></ul><p><br />R22104718<br />BeathChapman Pte Ltd<br />Licence no. 16S8112</p>",
